To build container:
    docker build -t yocto-build .


To run the container:
    docker run -it -v images:/home/yocto/workspace --name yocto-container yocto-build


Inside container:
    -   cd /home/yocto/poky/ && source oe-init-build-env && bitbake-layers add-layer ../meta-dspcoder
    -   bitbake dspcoder


To boot into qemu after build:
    qemu-system-x86_64   -m 1024   -nographic   -kernel /home/yocto/poky/build/tmp/deploy/images/qemux86-64/bzImage   -append "root=/dev/vda rw console=ttyS0"   -drive file=/home/yocto/poky/build/tmp/deploy/images/qemux86-64/dspcoder-qemux86-64.ext4,format=raw,if=virtio   -net nic -net user
